        "cnr_id": "comfy-core"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Measure, then auto-rebalance - one queue\n\n1. Pick your Anima files in the three loaders.\n2. Type your artists in the Pack node (left).\n3. Queue once. First render: the plain base image while the Layer\n   Probe measures each artist's real influence. The Probe Report\n   then emits a suggested_chain (weights that equalize the measured\n   influence) which feeds the second Pack - the second render IS\n   the rebalanced mix.\n\nRead the report text for the contribution split, per-step curves\nand the exact suggested weights."
      ]
    }
